<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-8606] sstablesplit does not remove original sstable</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-8606</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sstablesplit leaves the original file on disk, it should not.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
